    &= \sum_{\pi\in\Sym(9)} (\sgn\pi)\underbrace{\sum_{i=1}^{9}
       \alpha_{\pi(i)\pi(i)}}_{=\spur(a)=0}
       \xi_{\pi(1)\pi(2)\pi(3)} \eta_{\pi(4)\pi(5)\pi(6)} \zeta_{\pi(7)\pi(8)\pi(9)}
